Description:
Nest or invest in Officer
"Buy in the 3809 postcode with a fresh build that's ready to move in today."
Located opposite the pristine lake in Arcadia and right next to parkland the property at Zara Court is perfect for those that wish to be close to amenities. Walking distance to schools, shops and train station this property is earmarked as a wonderful investment or first home. This property will save you $$$. As a first home buyer you can expect the full saving on stamp duty . As an investor you can expect years of depreciation.
There are countless other benefits as well including the house itself that features:
- Three bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen with stone benchtops;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car remote garage with internal access;
- balcony with views overlooking the parkland and lake;
- Premier location among the complex.
